                            <comment id="12837417" author="jdcryans" created="Tue, 23 Feb 2010 19:56:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;One point of discussion here is whether we should only show the hit rate for cacheBlocks=true or both.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
