                            <comment id="12926516" author="hbasereviewboard" created="Sat, 30 Oct 2010 02:18:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Message from: &quot;Jonathan Gray&quot; &amp;lt;jgray@apache.org&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;-----------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
